                                                <h1>Defined Zones</h1>
                                                <p>Interact with the map or buttons to see more information about each zone.</p>
                                                <div class="zone zone-01" data-zone="1">
                                                    <h2 class="all-caps">Arrival</h2>
                                                    <ul class="dashed">
                                                        <li>Inviting and Intriguing Entry</li>
                                                        <li>Great street appeal</li>
                                                        <li>Doorman &amp; Bellman</li>
                                                        <li>Appropriate coverage for weather</li>
                                                        <li>Rest &amp; Pause waiting area</li>
                                                        <li>Luggage Cart Storage (immediate access path)</li>
                                                        <li>Access to security</li>
                                                        <li>Clear and concise wayfinding circulation</li>
                                                        <li>Subtle sense of time and place</li>
                                                        <li>Clear visibility into Lobby and Reception</li>
                                                    </ul>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="zone zone-02" data-zone="2">
                                                    <h2 class="all-caps">Reception</h2>
                                                    <ul class="dashed">
                                                        <li>Appropriate ratio of service stations to room count per <a href="#" class="inline-link">Hilton standards</a></li>
                                                        <li>Appropriate number of self-check in kiosks per <a href="#" class="inline-link">Hilton Standards</a></li>
                                                        <li>Waiting Area</li>
                                                        <li>Accessible Assistance</li>
                                                        <li>Easy access to back of house for staff</li>
                                                    </ul>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="zone zone-03" data-zone="3">
                                                    <h2 class="all-caps">GATHERING LOUNGE</h2>
                                                    <ul class="dashed">
                                                        <li>Various comfortable flexible types of lounge seating for groups and individuals</li>
                                                        <li>Seating groups suitable for light appetizers, afternoon/evening tea &amp; cocktails.</li>
                                                        <li>Physically removed from lobby but visually connected</li>
                                                        <li>A quiet and more residential space</li>
                                                        <li>Serviced Space</li>
                                                    </ul>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="zone zone-04" data-zone="4">
                                                    <h2 class="all-caps">KINETIC LOUNGE</h2>
                                                    <ul class="dashed">
                                                        <li>Easily transforms from Morning, Midday and Evening Functions</li>
                                                        <li>Visually captivating and enticing</li>
                                                        <li>Various types of lounge and bar seating for groups and individuals</li>
                                                        <li>Seating groups suitable for light appetizers, afternoon/evening tea &amp; cocktails.</li>
                                                        <li>Physically removed from lobby but visually connected</li>
                                                        <li>Serviced Space</li>
                                                        <li>Design savvy destination for local patrons</li>
                                                    </ul>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="zone zone-05" data-zone="5">
                                                    <h2 class="all-caps">Restaurant &amp; Bar</h2>
                                                        <ul class="dashed">
                                                            <li>Easily transforms from Morning, Midday and Evening Functions</li>
                                                            <li>Comfortable seating for groups and individuals</li>
                                                            <li>Seating groups suitable for informal dining, afternoon/evening tea &amp; cocktails.</li>
                                                            <li>Physically removed from lobby but visually connected</li>
                                                            <li>Serviced Space</li>
                                                            <li>Design savvy destination for local patrons</li>
                                                          </ul>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="zone zone-06" data-zone="6">
                                                    <h2 class="all-caps">Tech Lab</h2>
                                                    <ul class="dashed">
                                                        <li>Concierge Attendant</li>
                                                        <li>User-friendly self-help information access</li>
                                                        <li>Easy to use equipment for guest use</li>
                                                        <li>Plug in locations for guest charging</li>
                                                        <li>Freestanding dividers/screens to separate the Tech Lab from the rest of the lobby while remaining visually connected to Lobby activity</li>
                                                        <li>A residential library style and mood</li>
                                                        <li>Seating groups for private and casual meetings</li>
                                                        <li>Access to Assistance and Service Staff</li>
                                                    </ul>
                                                </div>
                                                <div class="zone zone-07" data-zone="7">
                                                    <h2 class="all-caps">The Market</h2>
                                                    <ul class="dashed">
                                                        <li>Gourmet product and food offerings</li>
                                                        <li>Innovative Grab &amp; Go and food display</li>
                                                        <li>Self-service food and beverage pick-up</li>
                                                        <li>Visual connection to guest elevators and lobby zones</li>
                                                        <li>Direct exit to building exterior</li>
                                                        <li>Short-term counter/perch seating</li>
                                                        <li>Some hotels may have bistro outdoor seating</li>
                                                        <li>Play on local culinary specialties, international flair in design and trends</li>
                                                        <li>Service staffed</li>
                                                    </ul>
                                                </div>
                                            </div>
